{"tid":309801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[紅火蟻來襲]日本揭發貨櫃還藏蟻后 來源:香港","createTime":"2017-07-05T10:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T05:39:41.000Z","uid":41351,"like":7,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9b6f9de30db641528ca6cfeea36c16bcea06cf","tid":309801,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:34:24.000Z","msg":"日本大阪發現一個來自香港的貨櫃有紅火蟻的蹤跡，並首次發現蟻后，是當地自5月以來，第四宗同類事件。<br />\n<br />\n日本環境省表示，上月尾在大阪市住之江區，一個從香港入口的貨櫃，發現另一種有毒的外來熱帶火蟻，之後在卸貨的大阪南港發現紅火蟻。環境省用殺蟲劑除蟲，並檢走部分紅火蟻調查，直到今周一證實有蟻后，懷疑已經結巢繁殖。<br />\n<br />\n日本國土交通省周二下令全國63個定期接收中國貨櫃的港口，採取措施滅蟻，其餘870個港口若接收中國貨櫃，亦要採取同樣措施。<br />\n<br />\n日本自從5月下旬，在兵庫縣尼崎市的貨櫃首次發現紅火蟻，其後再在神戶港及名古屋港，同樣來自廣州的貨櫃發現該種害蟲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1601264/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%B2%A8%E6%AB%83%E6%9C%89%E7%B4%85%E7%81%AB%E8%9F%BB+%E9%A6%96%E8%A6%8B%E8%9F%BB%E5%90%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1601264%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E6%25AB%2583%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B4%2585%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%259F%25BB%2B%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%259F%25BB%25E5%2590%258E&d=7bWjTqeFtcah%2FDfjGNVG0ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e0b67d8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1601264/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%B2%A8%E6%AB%83%E6%9C%89%E7%B4%85%E7%81%AB%E8%9F%BB+%E9%A6%96%E8%A6%8B%E8%9F%BB%E5%90%8E</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lanlix.com.tw/UploadFile/Disease/20121106155025_%E7%B4%85%E7%81%AB%E8%9F%BB_(1).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lanlix.com.tw%2FUploadFile%2FDisease%2F20121106155025_%25E7%25B4%2585%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%259F%25BB_%281%29.jpg&h=aa45179a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港竟然有紅火蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac