{"pid":"aaeddd6f3700d8babc4545ad48cbdf980c4425ec","tid":309801,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T01:45:23.000Z","msg":"香港啲紅火蟻咪又係支那度黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df4075b62215b6394aca4fb303a4eede60bd01b","tid":309801,"uid":38411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T01:56:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位請block樓豬</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4c924531735bcc200dea24d1d5d4da44e54a0b7e","tid":309801,"uid":118652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:00:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位請block樓豬</span></span></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9ecc7e6bcf33126cc768c97d17752dcfe6719fee","tid":309801,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:02:21.000Z","msg":"死5毛 blocked"},{"pid":"66a95d7c4edc353464625a2e77f61d7a18f1bb61","tid":309801,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位請block樓豬</span></span></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b0f13c6055b6c555b3faa5462270bcdab638e2a1","tid":309801,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:17:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾標題黨 又踩港"},{"pid":"ad06d7cb236bee709707551c3a70dfa3d1a771a2","tid":309801,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:35:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>光之練金術師呢隻支那五毛狗唔只一次用標呃人</blockquote><br />\n睇信報呢篇報導係話香港喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊有錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同樣來自廣州的貨櫃</strong></span></span>發現該種害蟲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】日本當局上月底在大阪市一個來自香港的貨櫃發現熱帶火蟻後，周二（4日）宣布在大阪南港發現更毒的南美紅火蟻，並首次找到蟻后，擔心這種可以致人於死地的毒蟻可能已在日本本土築巢繁殖。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當地政府如臨大敵，國土交通省隨即要求全國63個定期接收中國貨櫃的港口採取滅蟻措施，並呼籲其他870個港口若接收到中國貨櫃，亦要採取同樣措施。</span></strong>.......<br />\n<br />\n今次是在日本第4次發現紅火蟻，5月下旬在運至兵庫縣尼崎市的貨櫃箱內首次發現紅火蟻，隨後在神戶港及名古屋港相繼發現紅火蟻，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>這些紅火蟻都是透過從廣州運入日本的貨櫃「登陸」，環境省其後在全國7個主要港口展開調查。</strong></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170706/s00014/1499276934302\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170706%2Fs00014%2F1499276934302&d=7bWjTqeFtcah%2FDfjGNVG0ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ed48f5cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170706%2Fs00014%2F1499276934302&h=b44b0016\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170706/s00014/1499276934302</a>"},{"pid":"25b7dfa5dc9dd5e6e6c62fa29510461b9cc94ad1","tid":309801,"uid":3691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:39:16.000Z","msg":"hunter x hunter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281cceaf234010bca49fe772ac7140e7e89c1838","tid":309801,"uid":29001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即刻有bgm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n檔檔，檔定丁檔檔，鼎定叮丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n???"},{"pid":"c1dd82881016bdbdff2dabe170790d1e446eb541","tid":309801,"uid":29161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位請block樓豬</span></span></blockquote></blockquote></blockquo